FARMERS INSURANCE EXCHANGE et al. v. Ray Leon WOFFORD. No. 4641. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit April 3, 1953. Duke Duvall, Draper Grigsby and Charles. R. Nesbitt, Oklahoma City, Old., for appellants. Gus Rinehart, Oklahoma City, Okl, for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and. KNOUS, District Judge.

*692PER CURIAM.
